{"tid":532290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得依家個性格同自己好大出入？","createTime":"2018-01-17T16:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T11:48:25.000Z","uid":47671,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a3df3c8e83ec68e4d4c3d41cbcea1304494d1c32","tid":532290,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"姐係現實自己做緊嘅性格同自己理想嘅性格係唔成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我認為自己嘅性格已經愈嚟愈同理想嘅性格愈遠。<br />\n<br />\n根本我就唔係個咁嘅人，但我又控制唔到自己。<br />\n<br />\n但當靜落嚟嘅時候，就會諗返其實我根本就唔會做呢咁嘅野嘅人，跟住就會好唔開心因為本身理想吓性格唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知你地明唔明我講咩，唔識點表達呢種情況"},{"pid":"6871fc7bd1fd173b96189cd8cab9819d6e8060d0","tid":532290,"uid":150966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無辦法 會慢慢變成自己細個討厭嘅人做嘅野<br />\n現實迫着人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0119e4fb541c7fe04e07915b8af6ae34ca033ad","tid":532290,"uid":7954,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"922a7874edfb883dc66a0f87c2af6b877f2e0925","tid":532290,"uid":4859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"有時真係分唔清邊個先係真正嘅自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5233fd19475aac771c493db13b165522925bdba1","tid":532290,"uid":155455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"因為出黎社會做野逼自己假，但我其實好憎呢種人"},{"pid":"dff0607abe023fad196c3a4ab914575985fc4904","tid":532290,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6871fc7bd1fd173b96189cd8cab9819d6e8060d0","tid":532290,"uid":150966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"scor